HEADWORD: Subsizar
<hw>Sub*si"zar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An under sizar; a
student of lower rank than a sizar.</def> <mark>[Cambridge Univ.
Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Bid my <qex>subsizar</qex> carry my hackney to the buttery and
give him his bever.</q> <rj><qau>J. Fletcher.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subsoil</ent>⟦br⟧
